<emphasis id="09DDEA920D12B610FF4BF847FE94FBFA" bold="true" box="[136,274,1057,1083]" pageId="8" pageNumber="149">Description</emphasis>
:— 
<emphasis id="09DDEA920D12B610FEF5F844FEFCFBFD" box="[310,378,1058,1084]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="149">Herbs</emphasis>
with black stipular glands, very prominent on nodes, base of all leaves, bracts, and sepals.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
